China.
   16. Stuffed Dog Plush Toy, manufactured by unknown.
   17. Donald Duck Plush Toy, manufactured by Applause Inc.,
Woodland Hills, Calif.
   18. The Touchables Plush Toys, manufactured by Commonwealth Toy
&amp; Novelty Co., New York, N.Y.
   19. Christopher Teddy Bear Plush Toy, manufactured by The
Bearons of La Jolla, La Jolla, Calif.
   20. Alice VanderBear Plush Toy, manufactured by North American
Bear Company, Inc., Chicago, Ill.
   21. Push Toy, manufactured by Steven Manufacturing Company,
