41 partly cloudy; Miami 74 cloudy; New York 33 fair; Philadelphia
29 fair; Pittsburgh 31 cloudy; Portland, Maine 20 partly cloudy;
Richmond 27 fair; Tampa 59 partly cloudy; Washington, D.C. 33
partly cloudy.
   _Central: Birmingham 46 fair; Bismarck 28 fair; Chicago 38
windy; Denver 34 fair; Des Moines 41 fair; Indianapolis 39 cloudy;
Kansas City 45 partly cloudy; Little Rock 47 partly cloudy;
Louisville 42 fair; Memphis 47 fair; Nashville 43 fair; New Orleans
56 partly cloudy; North Platte 37 fair; Oklahoma City 54 windy;
Omaha 36 cloudy; Rapid City 31 partly cloudy; St. Louis 46 fair;
