San Antonio 59 partly cloudy.
   _West: Albuquerque 47 partly cloudy; Anchorage 19 partly cloudy;
Boise 30 fair; Casper 27 partly cloudy; Fairbanks 02 cloudy; Great
Falls 28 fair; Honolulu 75 fair; Las Vegas 52 partly cloudy; Los
Angeles 60 cloudy; Medford 33 foggy; Pendleton 42 cloudy; Phoenix
